+NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8080
+NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=https://[email]@sentry.io/[project-id]
+```
+
+## Getting Started
+
+```bash
+bun install
+bun run dev
 ```
 NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8080
 ```
